Source: parray-gin
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/theirix/parray_gin

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-parray-gin
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-parray-gin
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: PostgreSQL GIN support for arrays with partial match
  parray_gin adds GIN operator support for array values with partial-match
  semantics in PostgreSQL.
  It is useful for indexing and accelerating searches over array members where
  exact equality is not enough.
